tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I Dental in one word is definitely a one stop solution for all the dental problems. I was referred to Dr.Anil through a friend of mine, I would undoubtedly say that I received the best of treatment which was explained in detail by Dr.Anil and later followed by an excellent treatment plan.
He is so well organised that he also provides you the exact timing of appointment and never makes his patients wait. The best part in his treatment is that he also oversees the making of the teeth himself which makes the fitting of teeth quite perfect. On the top of all this the price that he quotes for the treatment is very reasonable when compared with other dentists.

I would heartfully thank Dr.Anil for the support and wonderful treatment that he offered which made my root canal treatment successful with out any pain nor discomfort.
I would recommend Dr.Anil and Idental to all those who have dental problems or want a thorough evaluation done. Believe me! This place and Dr.Anil are just amazing!.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Dental Cavities,Teeth Sensitive to Hot and Cold,Zirconia Crowns,Tooth Decay,Dental Fillings,
review: The beginning and the bottom up that I can comment is Excellent Service..Initially I consulted Dr.Anil Kumar Reddy two years back  when my wife had a severe pain due to wisdom tooth.. Like many others advise, I didnt get that suggestion of extracting the tooth in the first visit we had.. Rather the doctor guided us in the right direction of getting the surface soothened and he treated well that my wife continued to be normal for two years.. Recently a couple of months back when we visited for the same, he advised us to get it extracted only when he and we felt it better to be extracted.. During the process also, the way the doctor guided us, he suggests , he takes charge of the case are really appreciable.. The ease in the process the hospital adopts is the key benefit.. The patience levels of the doctor in listening to the problem and the attention towards the patient are really good.. The process is done in a single go..With that better experience we had, made me also to approach him for my filling and treatment of decayed teeth..In my case, it's more the best experience I had with the treatment and the result.. I suffered with pain inspite of getting the root canal treatment and fitting of crowns earlier, in an other reputed hospital at Hyderabad..But after getting the same done at I Dental I can only say a heartfelt big thanks to Dr.Anil Kumar Reddy and his team, for the ease in treatment,  advanced technol√≤gy and product, hospital ambience,  flexible timings, affordable cost,  more vitally the Doctor's Concern and Takeover of the problem, which is nevertheless the better than that of a Corporate Ambience... Besides that the prices and the cost of treatment is more economical and affordable in  comparison with many reputed hospitals that provide the same output, I feel like I got the best result at i Dental in all parameters of  efficiency...Thanks once again to Dr.Anil Kumar Reddy and his team and the hospital for all the things...I would definetely and satisfactorily refer any one who desires of getting the best result in treatment.. B V Bhargav Naidu..

tags: None
review: The best treatment i have got in the whole Secunderabad area, I happen to had got RCT done in the past at other clinics, but this time at iDental it's completely different they did it with at most care they are very clear and perfect, its not just about ambiance but they have got the right skill they have multiple dental chairs so wait time is relatively less.. Since past 15 years as a Dental Patient I have consulted many dental clinics across Secunderabad area and have faced issues like waiting long hours, reRCT, fragile bridge and caps lack of commitment to wards patients service.. At Idental I am happy to find answers to the problems I had faced...

reply_text:
Thank you sir for your positive feedback. I am extremely happy that I and I dental could resolve the issue to the best of your satisfaction. 
I really appreciate your patience and cooperation during the surgery. And post surgery too.
As you said we are very much well equipped with all the world class technology, and have all in-house manufacturing facilities for zirconium teeth, that gives an edge in price cutting and best quality to the patients at a lightening speed.
I once again thank you for calling me THE BEST DENTAL DOCTOR.
Looking forward to serve you and your near n dear again.

Doctor is very Friendly and polite , attended me with a warm welcoming smile. Diagnosis was perfect. Explained the needful treatment and is very patient with me as I am very anxious about the procedure.

Clinic portrays a corporate atmosphere and the charges are very minimal, best part of it is u can find a pricelist for every thing.
U can get Zirconium and ceramic teeth at a very cheaper price here.
I strongly recommend this clinic to all my near n dear.

review: After reading so many positive reviews we went to get our daughter's braces treatment done here. It went by very smoothly. Monthly appointments were properly initiated beforehand. We got to clear doubts if we had any, throughout the procedure too, and they were clarified. Dr. Anil Kumar Reddy sir was composed and always explained in a very informative and simplified way and gave us various options that we can look into if we had any hesitation, altogether he was pleasant and friendly. The staff was friendly and helpful too. Especially in the tough COVID times, the whole atmosphere was very well-maintained, precautions were taken to be safe. Our experience here was neat and we were satisfied.
